-- Croatia’s Petrokemija Signs Gas Supply Deal With E.ON Ruhrgas
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-07-30T10:44:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-30/croatia-s-petrokemija-signs-gas-supply-deal-with-e-on-ruhrgas.html
Petrokemija d.d. ,  Croatia ’s largest
fertilizer producer, signed a natural-gas supply contract with
E.ON Ruhrgas AG.  The contract will secure lower gas prices from August
through September this year and is diversifying gas supplies,
the company said today in a statement to the  Zagreb stock
exchange .  Spokesman Tomislav Pelin declined to elaborate when reached
by phone at the company’s headquarters in Kutina, Croatia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  